
## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Virtual Environment
venv/
env/

# Python Cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Environment Variables
.env

# Streamlit
.streamlit/

# VS Code
.vscode/

# Mac Files
.DS_Store

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary Files
temp/
tmp/

# Data Files
*.sqlite3

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Build Files
build/
dist/

# Secrets
secrets.toml

# JSON generated data
data.json